Mic spamming
[[Image:Micspam.jpg|right|thumb|Micspammers are beings of immense power.]]
'''Mic spamming''' is a secret [[Blowjob|technique]] created [[at least 100]] years ago by super trolls. It involves flooding the microphone chat on Steam games or Xbox Live by playing [[ghey]] music, [[Rape|ear raping]], [[Forced meme| forcing memes]], or other fail things that make the other [[faggots]] in the game go [[batshit insane]], all for the sake of great [[lulz]]. Subjects of mic spamming often include Hitler speeches, rick rolls, fresh prince. These are the most cliched and therefore [[unfunny]] things to spam over the mic, and people who do this should be forever regarded as the [[shit]] hole of the internet. A sign of a good mic spammer is not being able to hear anyone else in the server, except for the <strike>occassional</strike> [[I'm 12 years old and what is this?|12 year olds]] with their screeching, prepubescent voices that rightfully challenge the spam. 

== Where to mic spam ==

If you mic spam, there is a large chance you will get [[pwned]] by an admin. So, if you want to be successful, target only the games that contain raging niggers, [[Angry Homo Kid|flaming homos]] and [[republicans]]. Avoid [[Halo]] games, as for some unexplained reason, the people there actually know how to mute [[you]].
[[Image:Vehicles deployed.jpg|left|thumb|Intelligence.]]




Any game made by Valve however, due to them all being glitch-filled fails, are filled with some of the lowest life forms on the [[internet]], and will respond furiously to any agitation. Ironically, [[Retarded|many people on Steam think they are leet h4x0rs]], yet they complain about the true [[Internet Superheroes|internet heroes]] because they're too retarded to know how to mute someone, just showing you what kind of people Steam attracts.

